headline: Prologis (PLD) Tops Q3 FFO Estimates
summary: Prologis (PLD) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of +3.47% and -1.98%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
